From aae9fd49086126fe30bacb7321156ff74ce686a8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: patamin-lab <patamin@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 06:44:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Fix map pin drag, map-search form bug, PDF export 500,
 redesign PDF layout

- middleware.ts: exclude /fonts/* from auth check (fixed root cause of
  every PDF export 500 - react-pdf's server-side font fetch was being
  redirected to /login and getting HTML instead of font binary)
- map-view.tsx: make marker draggable with dragend handler so users can
  drag the pin instead of only re-clicking the map
- location-picker.tsx: remove nested <form> around map search (was
  bubbling submit up to the outer report form and bouncing to a new
  blank report); search button is now type=button, Enter key handled
  explicitly
- exportPdf.tsx: redesign single-record PDF to bordered key/value grid
  layout based on user-supplied reference reports; add RCA banner
  section, always-shown photo slots with placeholder for empty
  categories, video_link row (previously never surfaced), Thai status
  label (was showing raw English status code)
